    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College provides opportunities for each and everyone. It is not discriminative in anyway. And girls to boys ratio is almost like same. It may be higher for girls",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Overall it makes up for the best place for an all round and holistic development of a student.",
          "name": "Saumadip Das",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The compact batch sizs, only 69 students make it easy for me to interact with everyone and also the teacher can focus on everyone as well",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The exposure you get and the highly qualified faculties, whom I have only seen as eminent scholars or authors are now my professors.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "classrooms equipped with modern projectors and screens and so on, hence making up for a comprehensive learning environment.",
          "name": "Saumadip Das",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "St. Stephen's College is spread over a wide expense in the centre of the north Campus of Delhi University, being one of the oldest colleges in Delhi University the college is magnificent and is spread over 43 acres of land which speaks of its pride.",
          "name": "Angelina Ayushi Kenswar",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "College provides multiple societies. It has social service league, choreography society and many others.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has been A++ Naac accredited and stood 3rd in rank in the year 2024 in college ranking throughout India",
          "name": "Angelina Ayushi Kenswar",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college is vibrant being located in the heart of the North Campus with all the major colleges in close proximity.",
          "name": "Rohan Aryan Srivastava",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Not too many gym equipments as well the campus is too big",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The morning assemblies can be avoided. They still give me flashbacks from my school days.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "People her i disliked the most.tuey are judgemental",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I think in hostel, they can provide more facilities like common room and a dance room.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The obsession for perfection demanded by this institution, though that's what makes it special, can be very overwhelming for many.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The obsession for perfection demanded by this institution, though that's what makes it special, can be very overwhelming for many.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "while this is obviously a good thing under normal circumstances but the competition is cut throat for placements and internships among largely talented students.",
          "name": "Rohan Aryan Srivastava",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
